import { TextField } from "@mui/material"
import { useTzValidate } from "../MyHooks/UseTzValidate"
import { usePhoneValidate } from "../MyHooks/UsePhoneValidate"

export const Register = () => {

    let tzVal = useTzValidate()

    let phoneVal = usePhoneValidate()

    let passwordVal = use

    return <>
        <TextField id="tzInput" label="identity" variant="outlined" error={tzVal.tzErrorDisplay} onBlur={(e) => tzVal.checkTz(e)} helperText={tzVal.tzError} required />
        <TextField id="nameInput" label="user name" variant="outlined"></TextField>
        <TextField id="passwordInput" type="text" label="password" variant="outlined" error={passwordVal.passwordErrorDisplay} helperText={passwordVal.passwordError} required/>
        <TextField id="phoneInput" type="tel" label="phone" variant="outlined" error={phoneVal.phoneErrorDisplay} onBlur={(e) => phoneVal.checkPhone(e)} helperText={phoneVal.phoneError} />
        <TextField id="creditNumberInput" label="credit number" variant="outlined" required></TextField>
        <TextField id="validityInput" label="validity" variant="outlined" required></TextField>
        <TextField id="cvvInput" label="cvv" variant="outlined" required></TextField>
    </>
}
